nodes.text: Voystock was one of the guards of the Cog Hive Seven prison by the year 33 BBY. He was killed the same year at the same place by Jagannath. Before his death, he had a deal with the inmate Artagan Truax to get him and his son Eogan out of the prison.  During the escape attempt, he attempted to betray the Truax's, leading to his death by Maul's hands in the prison medbay.
